---
title: Golden-Crusted BBQ Tilapia Wraps with Marinated Cabbage and Potato Wedges
description: White fish pieces, topped with crispy shallots, are oven-baked until crisp before being wrapped in flour tortillas and crisp veggies. This wholesome family fave comes with a side of golden potato wedges and a BBQ-riffic dip!
